 Driver Drowsiness Detection System

Overview
The Driver Drowsiness Detection System is an intelligent safety application that detects driver fatigue in real-time using computer vision and deep learning techniques. The system monitors eye closure and facial features through a webcam and alerts the driver when signs of drowsiness are detected.

 Features
*  Real-time eye tracking using webcam
*  Instant alert system (sound/alarm)
*  Deep learning-based detection (YOLO / CNN)
*  Admin dashboard (if included)
*  User registration and login system
*  Database integration for storing user data

 Technologies Used

* Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* Backend: Python (Flask)
* Database: SQLite / MySQL
* Libraries & Tools:
  * OpenCV
  * TensorFlow / Keras
  * YOLO (You Only Look Once)
  * NumPy

