 Installation & Setup

1️⃣ Clone the repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/laharika-smarty/DrowsynessDetection.git
cd DrowsynessDetection
```

 2️⃣ Create virtual environment (optional but recommended)

```bash
python -m venv venv
venv\Scripts\activate   # On Windows
```

 3️⃣ Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

 4️⃣ Run the application

```bash
python app.py
```

 5️⃣ Open in browser

```
http://127.0.0.1:5000/
```

How It Works
1. The webcam captures live video of the driver
2. The system detects facial landmarks and eye movements
3. If eyes remain closed for a certain duration → drowsiness detected
4. An alert sound is triggered to wake the driver


